---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;

const title = "Privacy Policy | ConvertOcean Secure File Utility Portal";
const description = "Read our Privacy Policy to understand how ConvertOcean guarantees absolute file isolation, zero-telemetry, and complete data safety on your device.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} lang={lang} category="Privacy Policy" categorySlug="privacy">
  <style>
    .privacy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .privacy-lead {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--colors-body);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    .privacy-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    .privacy-subtitle {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.6px;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      color: var(--colors-ink);
    }
    .privacy-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--colors-body);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }
    .bullet-list {
      margin-left: 24px;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--spacing-xs);
      color: var(--colors-body);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>

  <main class="app-container" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-lg) var(--spacing-4xl); position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div class="privacy-container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy.</h1>
        <p class="privacy-lead">Your privacy is our core guarantee. ConvertOcean operates under a strict offline-first, client-side execution model to ensure your data stays yours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">1. 100% Client-Side File Processing</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          ConvertOcean converts, compresses, splits, and compiles your files entirely in your browser using JavaScript and WebAssembly compiled engines. 
          Your files are **never uploaded to, processed on, or stored on any external servers or databases**. All processing is executed by your device's local CPU/GPU inside sandboxed browser tab memory.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">2. Zero Telemetry & Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          We believe in complete user anonymity. We do not track, collect, or record any details regarding:
        </p>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Your files (file contents, filenames, sizes, extensions, or metadata).</li>
          <li>Your identity (we do not require accounts, signups, email verification, or payment methods).</li>
          <li>Your conversion history or utility usage statistics.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">3. Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          ConvertOcean does not use tracking cookies, targeting advertising trackers, or profiling algorithms. 
          We utilize local browser storage (`localStorage`) solely to store UI preferences, such as your dark mode settings (`light` / `dark`), ensuring a seamless experience when you return.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">4. External Libraries & CDN Integrity</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          Certain pages fetch script files (such as SheetJS for Excel spreadsheets or html2pdf for PDF compilations) via public CDN services. 
          These script assets are loaded by your browser solely to run the programs locally. CDNs do not receive or inspect your file data, which is parsed only after the script is loaded into your local browser window.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          Since ConvertOcean does not collect any personal data, our platform is completely safe for children and students to use for educational work and document processing without any risk of metadata profiling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2 class="privacy-subtitle">6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="privacy-text">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. However, our core commitment—that your files are never uploaded to any remote server and processing remains entirely client-side—is non-negotiable and will never change.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
